In fiscal 2023 and 2022, expenses recognized for short-term leases are €64 million and €56 million, respectively; expenses for low-value leases not accounted for under the right-of-use model are €27 million and €22 million, respectively. Sale and Leaseback transactions resulted in gains of €2 million and €94 million, respectively, in fiscal 2023 and 2022.

